===Noun===
{{la-noun|diēs|diei|diēī|m and f|fifth}}

# [[day]] {{gloss|any period of twenty-four hours}}
# day {{gloss|part of a day period between sunrise and sunset where one enjoys daylight}}
# {{context|often in the feminine|lang=la}} a set day or [[appointed]] time; [[date]], [[appointment]]

